Sentencas: For intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell (IT-SOFC) using hydrocarbon gases as fuels, the carbon deposition resistance of the anode is the most critical factor affecting its long-term stability.
Titulo: High-performance Ni in-situ exsolved Ba(Ce0.9Y0.1)0.8Ni0.2O3-δ/Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composite anode for SOFC with long-term stability in methane fuel

Sentencas: In this study, Ba(Ce0.9Y0.1)(0.8)Ni0.2O3-delta (BCYN) decorated Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 (GDC) composite is prepared by solution impregnation as anode for SOFC.
Titulo: High-performance Ni in-situ exsolved Ba(Ce0.9Y0.1)0.8Ni0.2O3-δ/Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composite anode for SOFC with long-term stability in methane fuel

Sentencas: And metal Ni nanoparticles are in-situ exsolved from BCYN as catalyst for the fuel gas cracking.
Titulo: High-performance Ni in-situ exsolved Ba(Ce0.9Y0.1)0.8Ni0.2O3-δ/Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composite anode for SOFC with long-term stability in methane fuel

Sentencas: At 750 degrees C, the polarization resistance of the optimized cell with Ni-BCYN/GDC composite anode are as low as 0.085 and 0.12 Omega cm(2) in H-2 and CH4, respectively.
Titulo: High-performance Ni in-situ exsolved Ba(Ce0.9Y0.1)0.8Ni0.2O3-δ/Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composite anode for SOFC with long-term stability in methane fuel

Sentencas: The related electrolyte-supported full cell's peak power density up to 211 mW cm(-2) can be achieved in CH4 at 750 degrees C.
Titulo: High-performance Ni in-situ exsolved Ba(Ce0.9Y0.1)0.8Ni0.2O3-δ/Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composite anode for SOFC with long-term stability in methane fuel

Sentencas: In the long-term polarization test (200 mA cm(-2)), single cell with Ni-BCYN/GDC composite anode maintains stable output for 100 h without obvious attenuation and carbon deposition.
Titulo: High-performance Ni in-situ exsolved Ba(Ce0.9Y0.1)0.8Ni0.2O3-δ/Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composite anode for SOFC with long-term stability in methane fuel
